name: Small Apartment 7
description:
Worldwide Webb Land in Tezos blockchain.
Worldwide Webb is an interoperable pixel art MMORPG metaverse game giving utility to popular NFT projects. 
The game uses NFTs for in-game avatars, pets, lands, items, and quests. Deployed with a build-first mentality by a group of crypto-native game developers, artists, coders, and marketers; rapidly pushing out new technologies and applications.
